    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This is to avoid your goal not typechecking anymore</p>",
        "id": 411773395,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1704731510
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You can probably work around this by using <code>subst hypS</code> instead of <code>rw</code>.</p>",
        "id": 411773634,
        "sender_full_name": "Patrick Massot",
        "timestamp": 1704731575
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If it did change <code>y</code> in place, your goal would have become <code>y ∈ {x : S | P}</code> while <code>y : {x : α | P}</code>. Since there's no <code>Mem (Set {x : S | P}) {x : α | P}</code>, this would fail.</p>",
        "id": 411773708,
        "sender_full_name": "Yaël Dillies",
        "timestamp": 1704731609
    }
